{"repository": {"pullRequest": {"number": 760, "title": "Update Python Example to Handle Third Level Domains and Higher", "body": "### Proposal\r\n- Add a new blocklist to check against wildcard domains\r\n- Update the verify.py script to filter against the public suffix list (e.g. *.co.uk)\r\n- Update the README.md to provide a basic python example of how the new blocklist can be used. Happy to update a couple of the other language examples that I am comfortable with if this is accepted\r\n\r\nFixes #759 \r\n", "baseRefName": "main", "baseRefOid": "3be7ff5b53f6e27afe5212e9f2a860c618b43382", "baseRepository": {"nameWithOwner": "disposable-email-domains/disposable-email-domains"}, "url": "https://github.com/disposable-email-domains/disposable-email-domains/pull/760", "createdAt": "2025-10-13T22:47:10Z", "mergedAt": "2025-10-16T17:09:26Z"}}, "base": {"repo": {"full_name": "disposable-email-domains/disposable-email-domains"}, "sha": "3be7ff5b53f6e27afe5212e9f2a860c618b43382"}, "diff_url": "https://github.com/disposable-email-domains/disposable-email-domains/pull/760.diff", "number": 760, "created_at": "2025-10-13T22:47:10Z", "merged_at": "2025-10-16T17:09:26Z", "resolved_issues": [759]}
{"repository": {"pullRequest": {"number": 772, "title": "feat(domains): add temp-mail.lol domains", "body": "Add temp-mail.lol disposable email domains\r\n\r\nThis commit adds five disposable email domains associated with temp-mail.lol:\r\n\r\n- disposely.xyz\r\n- disposly.com\r\n- fastestflex.com\r\n- temp-mail.lol\r\n- homecut.pro\r\n\r\nProof:\r\n<img width=\"1540\" height=\"1166\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e118648b-524d-4ece-bbdb-b61d7e10f0ec\" />\r\n\r\nYou can see this proof by entering https://temp-mail.lol/ and then clicking on the domains dropdown list.\r\n\r\nResolves #768", "baseRefName": "main", "baseRefOid": "f9623546cf938a30d8211ae7f08027d4244a1cd5", "baseRepository": {"nameWithOwner": "disposable-email-domains/disposable-email-domains"}, "url": "https://github.com/disposable-email-domains/disposable-email-domains/pull/772", "createdAt": "2025-10-31T03:58:13Z", "mergedAt": "2025-10-31T12:43:47Z"}}, "base": {"repo": {"full_name": "disposable-email-domains/disposable-email-domains"}, "sha": "f9623546cf938a30d8211ae7f08027d4244a1cd5"}, "diff_url": "https://github.com/disposable-email-domains/disposable-email-domains/pull/772.diff", "number": 772, "created_at": "2025-10-31T03:58:13Z", "merged_at": "2025-10-31T12:43:47Z", "resolved_issues": [768]}
