{"repository": {"pullRequest": {"number": 905, "title": "feat: add YoursToolsFetcher to fetch_domains.py", "body": "This pr adds fetching of `yours.tools` domains.\r\n\r\nAdded domains from yours.tools:\r\n\r\n> 01022.hk\r\n> 01130.hk\r\n\r\nIn this case, I didn't use the direct IP address because `apis.kyfudao.com` doesn't use Cloudflare, \r\nSo it won't block the GitHub worker's IP address.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"2250\" height=\"1184\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/9c5231ae-65af-421d-83dd-92ac01038a71\" />\r\n\r\nCloses #849", "baseRefName": "main", "baseRefOid": "3e784cdbfbdcdf8ca68b81af074fa6ca30f6b2e8", "baseRepository": {"nameWithOwner": "disposable-email-domains/disposable-email-domains"}, "url": "https://github.com/disposable-email-domains/disposable-email-domains/pull/905", "createdAt": "2026-03-17T09:59:35Z", "mergedAt": "2026-03-17T10:23:49Z"}}, "base": {"repo": {"full_name": "disposable-email-domains/disposable-email-domains"}, "sha": "3e784cdbfbdcdf8ca68b81af074fa6ca30f6b2e8"}, "diff_url": "https://github.com/disposable-email-domains/disposable-email-domains/pull/905.diff", "number": 905, "created_at": "2026-03-17T09:59:35Z", "merged_at": "2026-03-17T10:23:49Z", "resolved_issues": [849]}
